  <h2>1. Our role</h2>
  <p>Ivory Arc designs private, customised journeys and coordinates hotels, transport, guides and experiences on your behalf. We act as an organiser and agent arranging services that are owned and operated by independent third-party suppliers; we are not the principal provider of those services. Each supplier’s own terms and conditions apply to the services it provides, in addition to these Terms.</p>

