  <h2>4. Bookings and confirmation</h2>
  <p>A booking is confirmed, and a contract formed, only once we issue a written confirmation and the required advance has been received. Until then, no journey, rate or availability is guaranteed.</p>

  <h2>5. Payments</h2>
  <p>Payments are processed securely via Razorpay. Unless agreed otherwise in writing, journeys are secured with a 10% advance to confirm, 50% at least seven (7) days before departure, and the balance no later than 24 hours before departure. We may treat a journey as cancelled if scheduled payments are not received. Cancellations and refunds are governed by our <a href="/legal/refund-cancellation">Refund &amp; Cancellation Policy</a>.</p>

