  <h2>8. Travel insurance</h2>
  <p>Comprehensive travel insurance — covering at minimum medical expenses, evacuation, trip cancellation and curtailment — is strongly recommended and may be required for certain journeys. Travelling without adequate insurance is at your own risk.</p>

